<HEADLINE> AP Corrects Desegregation Story </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WASHINGTON (AP) -- In a May 17 story on the 45th anniversary of  
the Supreme Court's Brown vs. Board of Education decision, The 
Associated Press erroneously reported that a campaign to bolster 
affirmative action programs on college campuses was being launched 
by the White House. 
